  "title": "PRODUCTION MANAGER (CONSTRUCTION)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Coordinate with production teams for daily manufacturing plans.</li><li>Timely creation of manufacturing orders and forecasts for production scheduling.</li><li>Monitor manufacturing order production status and progress system.</li><li>Plan and release requisition based on planning parameter to ensure material availability.</li><li>Ensure inventory levels are within target ranges for key materials and key locations.</li><li>Manage order fulfilment till delivery, through coordination across the supply chain.</li><li>Understand short term capacity availability and constraints. Work with operations team to manage order fulfilment.</li><li>Take action regarding capacity and work progress changes in a timely manner, highlighting likely impact of these changes.</li><li>Monitor usage trends and customer forecasts for future purchases and capacity planning.</li><li>Report and follow up on aged inventory and status.</li><li>Review and provide reasons for deviation orders.</li><li>Evaluate and recommend settings for specific products based on actual parameters.</li><li>Participate actively in continuous improvement programs and take initiative to enhance material planning process.</li></ul><p>For interested applicants, please apply online or send your resume in WORD format to <strong>davidnhbsg@gmail.com; ram@deshingroup.com; wayne@deshingroup.com; shawn@deshingroup.com</strong></p><p>Thank you for your application but we regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified</p>",
